simulator.elevatormodules

Class DoorMotor

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.payloads.Networkable
      • simulator.elevatormodules.Module
        • simulator.elevatormodules.DoorMotor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeSensitive

    public class DoorMotor
extends Module
implements TimeSensitive
    Models the doors of the elevator in the simulation. Each object instatiated models one door. The Doors open and close via a simple velocity profile (they cannot instaneously change direction) and update their position to the outside world by sending DoorPosition messages.
